title: JP Software Take Command v18 00 Multilingual x64 Incl Keymaker-C
description: Take Command is a comprehensive interactive GUI and Windows command line toolkit that makes your Windows command prompts easier to use and far more powerful. Take Command includes optional Explorer-style integration, tabbed console windows, major enhancements to standard Windows CMD commands such as COPY, DEL, MOVE, SET, and START, and adds 160+ new commands, vastly improved command line editing and tab filename and directory completion, and thousands of other features
